name: Breakfast
description:
equal parts oatmeal and horlicks mix before pouring water, enough boiled water to to ensure the mixture is evenly soaked, leave on counter (~20 minutes) to ensure the oatmeal is softened to desirable texture.

Have almond soy milk on the side, may add some to the oatmeal and Horlick mixture.

name: supper
description: yogurt mixed with blueberries, sunflower seeds, and elusiyogurt mixed with blueberries, sunflower seeds, egusi seeds and chia seeds. with nuts and milk on side.

name: dinner
description:
with 40grams of sardines, a good dash of pepper, half teaspoon of turmeric, salt, stir than add eggs and stir again, 
just break the yolks and distribute it a litte, than add a slice of cheese to the top.

citrus fruits, apple and creatine on the side
